caption.text:
More than 5 years pretended I still have you for real. For more than 5 years I did all of my activities as if there were no problem without you. Actually, there were so many obstacles that I have done. More than 5 years the women in the right of this photo discussed with her own self in bringing up four children. For more than 5 years the girl in your left side grew up without a mature man that could be  admired and boasted by her. Not to be a melancholic boy (atau memang sudah melankolis). Tiba tiba aku mengingat bapak tengah malam waktu ngerjai karya ilmiah, tepatnya waktu buat narasi riwayat hidup penulis. Hehe, sebenarnya gak ada hubungannya.
Masih ingat dulu bapak khawatir sama ku, bahkan buat SMP yg naik angkotnya agak panjang sendiri gak berani, akhirnya SMP dekat SMA kakak. Hehe, rupanya kuliah disini sendiri aja berani. Padahal kak siska dulu mau bimbingan ke medan aja harus di antar dan di cek.
